nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE HEADING WESTWARD WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE HEADING WESTWARD WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII... As of 5:00 PM HST Wed Aug 06 the center of Henriette was located near 18.2, -132.4 with movement W at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
